{"tid":1865201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維珍澳洲航空永久停止香港航線","createTime":"2020-02-06T05:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T05:37:22.000Z","uid":29917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd78988dd795f7f73f49dfdc9c20460612ec156e","tid":1865201,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"維珍澳洲航空宣布永久停止香港航線。已於去年11月暫停的香港至墨爾本航線，將於2月11日取消。香港至悉尼航線則於3月2日取消。公司表示，社會動盪持續及區域爆發新型冠狀病毒疫情，導致乘客需求減少，因而作出有關決定，又指有關航線已不再商業上可行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bonbontech.com/Blog/Detail/title/維珍澳洲航空退出香港市場永久停止香港航線\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbonbontech.com%2FBlog%2FDetail%2Ftitle%2F%E7%B6%AD%E7%8F%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%B7%9A&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=ee7a37ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://bonbontech.com/Blog/Detail/title/維珍澳洲航空退出香港市場永久停止香港航線</a>"},{"pid":"23eebf16cadedecb088ff016b053fac6ef4fb672","tid":1865201,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c3fa3e5833a8172957bb2bf3fce28eb6f81fff","tid":1865201,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}